# Examine bunching
# Zoom in on just the first cut (above/below 643 with 19.099 bandwidth of the cutoff)

dat<- dat %>%
  filter(api_rank >= (643-19.099)& api_rank <= (643+19.099))

bunch <- dat %>%
  ggplot(aes(api_rank)) +
  geom_bar(fill = "cyan3") +
  geom_vline(xintercept = 643, color = "red") +
